{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act12side", "eventName": "多索雷斯假日", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "DH-7", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "沙灘阻擊", "storyInfo": "真正的主謀潘喬佔領了船隻，並發表了奪取城市的宣言。\n沙灘上，星熊等人發現有人想刺殺市長，趕去幫忙。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$farce_intro", "key": "$farce_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_200"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咦，節目的內部線路怎麼接不上了？", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_200"}, {"id": 10, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是......被佔用了？", "name": "工作人員"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_200"}, {"id": 11, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "image", "attributes": {"image": "20_I00", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$darkalley_intro", "key": "$darkalley_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_transmissionget", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 3.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "name": "avg_npc_192_1#6", "style": "cutin", "fadestyle": "horiz_expand_center", "fadetime": 0.5, "width": 200.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "十年前，我相信只要把聯合政府和辛嘉斯王朝都趕出去，玻利瓦爾就會獲得和平。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我為了真正玻利瓦爾人打生打死。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "最後，我三千個弟兄被我帶去送死，如果不是我的老哥哥豁出性命，我那天就被槍決了。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "從那天起，我就明白了。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聯合政府，辛嘉斯王朝的貴族們，真正玻利瓦爾人，這三個沒有一個真的想要拯救玻利瓦爾，他們只是在打仗。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們再打多少年，玻利瓦爾也不會有救。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為了避難，我逃到了這座城市。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後，我發現，在這個已經沒救的國家裡，還有這樣一座沒救的城市。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉·桑切斯，比他們所有人都更加不可救藥。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她在這片沒救的土地上建立了這座比所有玻利瓦爾城市加起來都要腐敗的城市。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她不僅自己享受其中，還將其他人也拉到自己身邊和她一起享受。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所有人都被她捲了進來，過著自以為體面的日子。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們根本不知道這座城市的下水道裡流淌著多少惡臭的人血，飼養了多少的食腐餓獸。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "她吸食著生活在這片土地上的人民的血肉，而絲毫不關心他們的死活。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座城市他媽的該死，在這裡享樂的你們也他媽的該死！！！", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "大獎賽結束了。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來，我會奪取這座城市。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒人拯救這個國家，我來。", "name": "潘喬"}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "CharacterCutin", "attributes": {"widgetID": "1", "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "bg_20_G06", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以你的父親才是這一切的主謀。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1"}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "當你發現我們有可能察覺到什麼的時候，你選擇將我們的注意力轉移到你的身上。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣，即使我們真的發現了什麼，你也為你背後的人爭取了時間。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1"}, {"id": 60, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是的。我不想說我贏了，陳小姐，這本來就不是一場公平的較量。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1"}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你們來得太晚，接受坎黛拉女士的委託又太匆忙。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我最後的善意，陳小姐，和林小姐投降吧。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1"}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "兩位要是願意收手，我保證沒有人會傷到你們。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這裡的事和你們無關，你們沒有必要參與到這樣一場沒有對錯可言的事情中。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1"}, {"id": 66, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我做不到。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2"}, {"id": 68, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1#2", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這艘船已經被我們的人佔領了，反抗的話，你和林小姐會死的。", "name": "埃內斯托"}, "figure_art": "avg_486_espumo_1"}, {"id": 70, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_1013_spchen_1", "name2": "avg_486_espumo_1", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "有個老朋友說過，只有被狠狠捶打過一遍，我才會像過去的她一樣，知道自己那些可笑的執著都不過是些衝動。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1"}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我到現在也還沒有分清，哪些是可以堅持的執著，哪些是不切實際的衝動。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1"}, {"id": 73, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我想她應該也是知道的，如果因此我就不去做的話，我也就不叫陳暉潔了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1"}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "動手吧，我趕時間。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_1013_spchen_1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$frontline_intro", "key": "$frontline_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_201"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，這不是潘喬先生嗎？他在說什麼？", "name": "震驚的男遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_202"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不知道，是什麼特別演出嗎？", "name": "震驚的女遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0, "ystrength": 40.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 255.0, "g": 255.0, "b": 255.0, "fadetime": 0.05, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_explo_n"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_201"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哪裡來的爆炸聲？！", "name": "害怕的男遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_202"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好像是第一輪的城區那邊！你看，那邊冒煙了！", "name": "害怕的女遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_202"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_201"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂喂喂，不是吧，難道潘喬這個老頭是來真的？！", "name": "害怕的男遊客"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_201"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_207", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉女士，城內和郊區出現了多股不明勢力正在引發混亂。", "name": "護衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 106, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_207", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......嘖嘖，來這招啊，我的老潘喬。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#2"}, {"id": 108, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_207", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "坎黛拉女士，請前往安全的地方避難。", "name": "護衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_207", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 111, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "避難？說什麼呢，這裡可是頭等座，我哪裡都不會去。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "城裡那些突然冒出來的傢伙隨便應付一下就好了，反正他們的目的最後都會是我。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#1", "name2": "avg_npc_207", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，疏散群眾還是要做的，不過，城門先封閉了，讓他們都回到自己的住所去。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "然後嘛，把工作人員保護起來。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓他們籌備宴會，還有繼續進行大獎賽的轉播。", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_207", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "保護好他們，別讓我的大獎賽被破壞了，明白了嗎？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#4"}, {"id": 120, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_207", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的。", "name": "護衛"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_207"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_198_1#3", "name2": "avg_npc_207", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對了對了，去調一批新的無人機來，船上的那些估計被他們破壞了，這麼有趣的事情，怎麼能錯過呢？", "name": "坎黛拉"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_198_1#3"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "fadetime": 0.5}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#4", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，不是吧，我們只是來度個假，還能遇到這種事？", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#4"}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "雖然應該說，這才有玻利瓦爾的感覺。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#2"}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#2", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別貧了，快想想怎麼辦。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#4"}, {"id": 140, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#4", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "Missy，我們現在只是遊客，管不了也不該管這麼多。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要是陳暉潔站在這裡，你會這麼對她說嗎？", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#6"}, {"id": 144, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#6", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "會啊，只是你也知道她的答案。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼我的答案也是一樣的。", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#2"}, {"id": 148, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，我只能說，我不反對。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1"}, {"id": 150, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#2", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "羅德島......嘖，鑄鐵剛好去買飲料了，我去看看。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1#5"}, {"id": 152, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#5", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且她們兩個現在還在船上呢，我怎麼可能放心走啊！", "name": "詩懷雅"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_197_1#5"}, {"id": 154, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1", "name2": "avg_npc_197_1#5", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我倒是不怎麼擔心她們兩個就是了。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1"}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，我們是局外人，沒有感覺很正常，但是既然有這樣的事情發生，我不信老陳和林小姐會一無所知。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "現在也不知道船上具體的狀況，我們想要上船幫老陳她們也不太現實，還是做些力所能及的事。", "name": "星熊"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_203_1"}, {"id": 158, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "largebg", "attributes": {"imagegroup": "bg_20_G04_1/bg_20_G04_2", "solidwidth": "920/920", "solidheight": 720.0}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194"}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "遊客A？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 168, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_195"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "遊客B？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_195"}, {"id": 170, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#4"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖，居然趁我雙手拿飲料的時候偷襲。", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#4"}, {"id": 172, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#6"}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（沒想到居然會發生這樣的事。）", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#6"}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（對方看起來是有組織的，沙灘上已經陷入了混亂。）", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#6"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（現在武器也不在手邊，難以施展，先去和星熊她們會合......）", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#6"}, {"id": 176, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_npc_195", "focus": 1.0}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "一起上。", "name": "遊客A？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_194"}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_194", "name2": "avg_npc_195", "focus": 2.0}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好。", "name": "遊客B？"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_195"}, {"id": 180, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_206_1#2"}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嘖！", "name": "鑄鐵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_206_1#2"}, {"id": 182, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 185, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "char_empty"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$rungeneral", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "fadetime": 0.3, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.51}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "characteraction", "attributes": {"name": "middle", "type": "move", "xpos": 200.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "false"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {"name": "avg_npc_203_1#6", "fadetime": 0.7}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}